3.28.3 / 3.30.3
===============

* shell: Adjust colors
* Various small fixes
* Add support for gnome 3.30 (gtk+ 3.24)

3.28.2
======

* gtk2/gtk3: Adjust selection color;
* gtk2/gtk3: New scrollbars (vintage scrollbars cant be displayed correctly in libreoffice);
* gtk3/gtk2/shell: Adjust assets to match new colors;
* gtk3: Adjust undershoot size;
* gtk3: Revert workaround for popover menus;
* gtk3: Add missing backdrop states;
* gtk3: New pathbar style for nautilus
* shell: Change font to Liberation Sans, Arimo;
* shell: Adjust selection color;
* general: Installation now requires meson and sasc;
* general: Revert meson to build theme;
* general: Build cleanup.

3.28.1
======

* gtk3/gtk2: Border color adjustment (improve contrast);
* gtk3/gtk2: Scrollbar color adjustment; 
* gtk3: Transform apps.css to scss;
* gtk3: Messagedialog decoration fix;
* gtk3: Scrollbar animation fix;
* gtk3: Add undershot effect, revert removing of overshoot;
* gtk3: Nautilus operation button style edit;
* gtk2: Tooltip fix, now they have borders;
* shell: Notification button tweak.


3.28.0.1
========

* Build changes: meson no longer builds the theme, just installs -
  workaround for users, who want just copy theme folder, without using meson;
* shell: Change font to roboto. 


